race.comment: GREYT THINKER (2) raced on pace and kept going to score by 1.7L over 1300m at Hawkesbury in Maidens. He was heavily backed and stripping fitter can take the next step. EAGLES BEWARE (1) has switched yards and resumes off a big heavily bet Maiden win at Queanbeyan. He's had two trials and won't have to be much improved to feature. ROYAL BOMBADIER (8) missed a nose here improving again and then came back and was plainer. He's better than that and is worth another chance. NANTUCKET ISLAND (5) resumes and will race over further. Will likely need it but she has talent and the betting will be key with her.
